OL,3,C'No justice': Drug-taking driver who
OL,4,Ckilled student in hit-and-run jailed
OL,6,FA driver who killed a university
OL,7,Fstudent in a hit-and-run crash while
OL,8,Fon drugs has been jailed.
OL,10,FOliver Pryde was hit by Adam Smith's
OL,11,FVauxhall Corsa on Penistone Road,
OL,12,FHuddersfield, on 12 July 2021. The 18-
OL,13,Fyear-old was thrown into the path of
OL,14,Fanother car in the carriageway.
OL,16,FSmith, from Huddersfield, fled the
OL,17,Fscene but was arrested a short time
OL,18,Flater.
