OL,3,C'No justice': Drug-taking driver who
OL,4,Ckilled student in hit-and-run jailed
OL,6,FHe was nearly twice the legal limit
OL,7,Ffor drugs and was unlicensed and
OL,8,Funinsured.
OL,10,FThe 33-year-old was charged with
OL,11,Fcausing death by careless driving when
OL,12,Funfit through drugs and while
OL,13,Funlicensed and uninsured.
OL,15,FSmith denied the offences but was
OL,16,Ffound guilty after a six-day trial at
OL,17,FLeeds Crown Court.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for 10 years and banned
OL,20,Ffrom driving for nine years.
