OL,3,C'No justice': Drug-taking driver who
OL,4,Ckilled student in hit-and-run jailed
OL,6,FMr Pryde, from Cumbria, was the eldest
OL,7,Fof four children and studying maths at
OL,8,FHuddersfield University.
OL,10,FHis heartbroken family said there was
OL,11,F"no justice" over his death.
OL,13,FHis mother Stacey, said: "Oliver
OL,14,Fwanted to become a maths teacher at
OL,15,Fhis old secondary school. His words
OL,16,Fwere that he wanted to teach others
OL,17,Fand inspire the next generation.
