OL,3,C'No justice': Drug-taking driver who
OL,4,Ckilled student in hit-and-run jailed
OL,6,F"No justice will ever be served in my
OL,7,Feyes. I am left with a lifetime
OL,8,Fwithout Oliver and I'm left trying to
OL,9,Frebuild the family that this person
OL,10,Fbroke."
OL,12,FDet Con Mark Turner, of West Yorkshire
OL,13,FPolice, said Smith's actions left
OL,14,FOliver's family and friends
OL,15,F"devastated and deprived Oliver of a
OL,16,Fpromising future".
OL,18,F"I hope this highlights the dangers
OL,19,Fand consequences of drug driving," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
